Update step types and create the SharedFields component that all editors will use.

## Working Directory
`Code&DBs/Workflow/surfaces/app/src/builder/`

## Task 1: Update stepTypes.ts

Read `stepTypes.ts` first. Add these types and fields:

```typescript
export interface NotificationChannel {
  id: string;
  kind: 'email' | 'slack_webhook' | 'sms' | 'webhook' | 'in_app';
